extendedInfo.description: Domestic and Family Violence Protection Act 2012 - A guide for service providersThis app is a guide to the Domestic and Family Violence Protection Act 2012 (Queensland). It is a tool for appropriately qualified domestic and family violence support workers* and other professionals working in the area of domestic and family violence, such as police, lawyers and court staff. Keep the Act in your pocket, whenever you need it! The app will provide quick and easy access to the sections of the Act and a concise summary of the information you are looking for. *If you are experiencing domestic or family violence, please obtain legal advice from a lawyer and assistance from a specialised domestic and family violence support service. If you fear for your safety, contact the police.
